- True!
- True!

155
00:08:30,448 --> 00:08:32,089
- Return the land!
- Return the land!

156
00:08:32,209 --> 00:08:33,768
We will definitely refund you.

157
00:08:33,969 --> 00:08:36,089
Those who want a refund,
please fill out the forms.

158
00:08:36,129 --> 00:08:38,089
We'll return the principal
plus interest.

159
00:08:38,449 --> 00:08:41,129
