- What does it mean?

166
00:08:54,849 --> 00:08:55,568
What does it mean?

167
00:08:56,369 --> 00:08:57,329
What else could it mean?

168
00:08:57,528 --> 00:08:58,489
It means no.

169
00:08:59,408 --> 00:09:00,729
That's not what I meant.

170
00:09:01,168 --> 00:09:02,609
Since the founding of Yuehai,

171
00:09:02,768 --> 00:09:04,969
