189
00:09:48,568 --> 00:09:50,249
We're not here to eat!

190
00:09:50,688 --> 00:09:51,609
- Exactly!
- Right!

191
00:09:51,609 --> 00:09:52,369
Alright then,

192
00:09:52,528 --> 00:09:54,489
